<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Goofy Store</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset some default styles */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        /* Navbar styles */
        .navbar {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #624E88;
            height: 50px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        .navbar ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
        }

        .navbar li {
            margin: 0 15px;
        }

        .navbar li a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .navbar li a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        /* Body styles */
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background-color: #f0f4f8;
            color: #333;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            padding-top: 70px; /* To account for the fixed navbar */
        }

        /* About container */
        .about-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            width: 90%;
            padding: 20px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        /* Heading styles */
        h1 {
            color: #4a4e69;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #22223b;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        /* Paragraph styles */
        p { 
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #555;
        }

        /* Footer styles */
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #555;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }

        /* Link styles */
        a {
            color: #9a8c98;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        a:hover {
            color: #4a4e69;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="navbar">
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/">Goofy Store</a></li>
            <li><a href="/cart">Cart</a></li>
            <li><a href="/personal">Me!</a></li>
            <li><a href="/about">About Us</a></li>
        </ul>
    </div> 

    <div class="about-container">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <h2>Welcome to Goofy Store!</h2>
        <p>At Goofy Store, we believe in providing the best products at the best prices. Our mission is to bring joy and convenience to your shopping experience.</p>
        <p>We carefully curate our collection to ensure quality and style. Whether you're looking for the latest trends or classic essentials, we have something for everyone.</p>
        <p>Thank you for choosing us! We are excited to serve you.</p>
        <p>For inquiries, please <a href="/contact">contact us</a>.</p>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>Copyright Â© (All Rights Reserved under our policy )</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
